com.danielly.jsf.cinema.checkout

Class ShoppingCartLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.checkout.ShoppingCartLine

  • public class ShoppingCartLine
extends java.lang.Object
    The class ShoppingCartLine holds the information about a specific ticket the user wish to purchase. It contains the information about the showtime, the movie, hall and the seat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gil Danielly
